title: Grateful Dead Live at St. Paul Civic Center on 1983-06-25
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Cassidy, West L.A. Fadeaway, My Brother Esau, Big Railroad Blues, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Might As Well

Set 2

Touch Of Gray-> Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Women Are Smarter, Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Throwing Stones-> Black Peter-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> One More Saturday Night, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
